    <label>elephant spear</label>
    <description>The elephant spear is crafted using the tusks of an elephant, and is typically a status symbol reserved for head hunters or leaders of a tribe. The shaft is engraved with minor enchantments, further boosting the combat abilities of the user.
		
This weapon is enchanted and provides additional benefits to trained mages and fighters:
Max Energy: +10%
Damage Boost: +10%
Arcane Resistance: +20%</description>
